output_list.criticism: The buyTokens function in the SpadeIco contract has an integer overflow vulnerability. The 'tokensToSell' variable is incremented by 'tokens' without any check to ensure it does not exceed 'TOKENS_FOR_SALE'. This allows the 'icoAgent' to set 'tokensToSell' arbitrarily, aka the 'trade' function in the icoAgent contract.
